learn to embrace it as myself.

96
00:07:32,786 --> 00:07:36,123
I can therefore say without reservation

97
00:07:36,206 --> 00:07:37,833
that I have grown through love.

98
00:07:38,417 --> 00:07:41,587
When I was struggling,
