but in hindsight,

103
00:07:50,220 --> 00:07:52,598
having someone in the same boat
who empathized with me,

104
00:07:52,681 --> 00:07:54,892
and hearing those words

105
00:07:55,184 --> 00:07:57,769
was a huge help to me.

106
00:07:58,437 --> 00:08:05,027
So in the hope of giving
that kind of consolation to someone else,

107
00:08:05,110 --> 00:08:09,072
I mustered the courage
to come back to the show like this.

108
00:08:09,615 --> 00:08:12,951
Come to think of it,
I haven't thanked that person yet.

109
00:08:13,535 --> 00:08:15,996
I'd like to take this chance
to tell the person

110
00:08:16,079 --> 00:08:21,376
