I want to tell you this.

113
00:08:30,677 --> 00:08:32,387
I've been there.

114
00:08:33,096 --> 00:08:36,767
A breakup, like the common cold,
is not a big deal.

115
00:08:36,850 --> 00:08:39,144
This too shall pass.

116
00:08:39,228 --> 00:08:40,646
You will get well soon.

117
