I tried not to show it.

244
00:17:51,821 --> 00:17:53,406
Maybe I was tired of that.

245
00:17:58,620 --> 00:18:00,413
We all are.

246
00:18:01,039 --> 00:18:02,916
No one is perfect after all.

247
00:18:04,083 --> 00:18:05,126
You were.

248
00:18:06,461 --> 00:18:09,756
